    "Electroporation was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.",
    "200 µl PBS containing 10 7 cells/mL and 1 µM siRNA or 10 µg/ml plasmid DNA was electroporated in a 0.2-cm cuvette using a 150 V, 10 ms, and 1 pulse program.",
